title: Goodbye Childhood Memories
itunes:title: Goodbye Childhood Memories
description:
Wednesday 3/21- It is True it is not fake news, one of our most loved childhood memory is gone! Toys R Us is shutting down! but does anyone care? The Breakfast Club opened up the phone lines too see if any of our listeners were devastated by the news. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a custodian who took advantage of the National School Walkout by stealing $180 dollars from students' book bags, and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
